criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with initial diagnosis of follicular lymphoma,
             refractory/relapsed/transformed after first line therapy;

          -  All stages at the time of relapse;

          -  Histological grade 1-3a at the time of initial diagnosis;

          -  Age over 18 years;

          -  Availability of clinical data, including baseline information, comorbidities, data on
             disease localization, laboratory parameters at staging, features of treatment adopted
             and assurance of follow-up updating as requested

          -  Diagnostic material available for review;

          -  Written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        • Age < 18 years
